reviewText: When you think of all naturals and your given a cover of a well endowed female, and you are aware of playboys history with visually gifted females well you would think the video would feature such women, well not the case here.  The filming was much to close with very little whole body shots, it seems they did this one on the cheap with only one camera that had the zoom feature stuck on max.  Additionally the interview segments were an annoyance and bother and did nothing for the women being interviewed, as the interviewing hosts seemed to just spill out the lamest questions and opinions. Finally they could have featured more girls or an additional video of each girl. Overall I would have to say the best thing about this video was the cover image.
